[Hotkeys]
Launch DbDo=Alt+Control+D, Launch or activate the DbDo application via a Windows desktop shortcut
Hotkey Summary=Alt+Shift+H, Display this list of command names, hot keys, and descriptions in a new window

; --- File ---
New Database=None
Add Table=None
Open Database=Control+O
Open Recordset=Control+Shift+T
Recent Files=Alt+R
Save Database=Control+S
Close Database=Control+W
Backup Database=None
Compare Database=None
Import=Alt+I
Merge=Alt+M
Export Data=Alt+X
Out Printer=Control+P
Select Table=F7
Select View=None
Switch Table=Alt+F6
Switch Previous Table=Alt+Shift+F6
Switch Object=Control+F6
Switch Previous Object=Control+Shift+F6
Exit Application=Alt+F4

; --- Edit ---
New Record=Control+N
Edit View=Control+E
Edit Cell=F2
Delete Record=Control+D, or Delete
Delete Record Force=Control+Shift+D
Copy Record=Control+Shift+C
Append Record=Alt+Shift+C
Copy Record as New=Control+Shift+N
Send Mail=None
Replace Column=Control+R
Regex Replace=Control+Shift+R
Set Mark=Control+M
Say Mark=Shift+M
Toggle Marked=Control+Space
Edit Notes=Control+F9
Edit Tags=Control+T
Edit URL=Control+U
Clear Mark=Control+Shift+M
Set Mark All=Control+A
Clear Mark All=Control+Shift+A
Invert Marked=Alt+Shift+I
Start Mark=F8
Complete Mark=Shift+F8
Start Unmark=Alt+F8
Unmark Range=Alt+Shift+F8
Save Bookmark=Control+B
List Bookmarks=Alt+B
Clear Bookmark=Control+Shift+B
Open Cell=Control+Enter
Open URL=Control+Shift+U
Pick Value=Control+F2

; --- Navigate ---
Step Record First=None
Step Record Last=None
Step Record Next=None
Step Record Previous=None
Set Position=Control+G
Repeat Set Position=Alt+G
Find=Control+F
Find Previous=Control+Shift+F
Jump Record=Control+J, or Shift+J
Jump Previous Record=Control+Shift+J
Find Regex=Control+F3
Find Previous Regex=Control+Shift+F3
Search Next=F3
Search Previous=Shift+F3
Enter Child=Alt+RightArrow, or Enter
Exit Child=Alt+LeftArrow, or Backspace
Exit Child to Root=Alt+Home

