Say Goto=Shift+G
Say Yield=Shift+Y
Say Tables=Shift+F7
Say Marked=None
Say Edited=Shift+E
Say Notes=Shift+N
Say Tags=Shift+T
Say Column Rest=Control+L
Say Column Rest Marked=Control+Shift+L
Say Records Rest=Alt+L
Say Records Rest Marked=Alt+Shift+M
Say Marked Rows=Shift+Space
Say Sort Filter=Shift+8, or NumPadStar
Say Position=Alt+Delete
Say Clipboard=Alt+Apostrophe
Say Yield Marked=None
Say Added=Shift+A
Say Cell=Shift+C
Say Filter=Shift+F
Say Select=Shift+S
Say Query=Shift+Q
Say ID=Shift+I
Say Look=Shift+L
Say Related=Shift+R
Say URL=Shift+U
Filter Records=Alt+Shift+F
Reset Filter=None
Filter Regex=None
Reset Sort=None
Order Records=Alt+O
